rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Me and Rita had a fight.
First one I can remember.

rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0002
rows.name:
She insisted on staying in Iira to
help out, but I told her straight -
we don't need her.

rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I know my place is here. Iira's
where I belong.

rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0004
rows.name:
But there's no reason for that girl
to get herself any more mixed up
in our business here.

rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0005
rows.name:
She's got her own goals. Said
she wants to be a Driver like Laura.
Well that's fine by me.

rows.label: tlk70000022_05_msg0006
rows.name:
But she won't get there staying here.
It's time for her to get out there,
see the world.
